PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772182876
OL,3,C'We've got nowhere': Families react to
OL,4,Cdamning maternity findings
OL,6,FLyn has now testified at two major
OL,7,Finquiries looking at East Kent
OL,8,Fmaternity services. She has little
OL,9,Ffaith this review will be different.
OL,11,F"It was heartbreaking and knowing that
OL,12,Fafter nearly nine years, we've got
OL,13,Fnowhere", Lyn Richardson told ITV News
OL,14,FMeridian.
OL,16,F"We are relying now on Baroness Amos
OL,17,Fto do what they promised, what this
OL,18,Fgovernment promised to do, which is
OL,19,Fuse prophylactic methods to prevent
OL,20,Fbirth trauma, mental illness,
OL,21,Fperinatal mental illness and suicide.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@HO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
