OL,3,C'We've got nowhere': Families react to
OL,4,Cdamning maternity findings
OL,6,FWatch: Lyn Richardson tells ITV
OL,7,FMeridian that the latest findings are
OL,8,Fdevastating.
OL,10,F"It just, it breaks everybody down. I
OL,11,Fmean, losing Becky to suicide was bad
OL,12,Fenough. It devastates not just the
OL,13,Ffamily, but her friends, communities.
OL,15,F"It's very costly too, you know, in
OL,16,Fterms of I think #12.5 billion is the
OL,17,Festimated cost to society now,
OL,18,Fperinatal ill health, mental health,
OL,19,Fsorry, and suicides.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
