PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772182876
OL,3,C'We've got nowhere': Families react to
OL,4,Cdamning maternity findings
OL,6,F"We are worn out and we don't want to
OL,7,Fbe another case of just giving up
OL,8,Fbecause we're so exhausted and ill
OL,9,Fwith the fragmentation that it causes
OL,10,Fwithin the family, within our
OL,11,Fcommunities, because the stress is
OL,12,Fjust inestimable.
OL,14,F"At the end of the day, you've got a
OL,15,Fmother and a baby who've suffered,
OL,16,Favoidably, unnecessarily, it doesn't
OL,17,Fhave to happen.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
