CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772182876
OL,3,C'We've got nowhere': Families react to
OL,4,Cdamning maternity findings
OL,6,F"And I can tell you that yesterday,
OL,7,Fbefore I went to this conference, I
OL,8,Fwent to Nonington Churchyard with my
OL,9,Fson and my sister, Becky's godmother,
OL,10,Fjust to lay some flowers.
OL,12,F"We remember her every day, she's with
OL,13,Fus. And we just don't want this to
OL,14,Fhappen to anybody else, it's
OL,15,Funnecessary, because birth trauma,
OL,16,Fit's a splinter that festers and
OL,17,Fresults in ill mental health and
OL,18,Fsuicide."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
