OL,3,C'We've got nowhere': Families react to
OL,4,Cdamning maternity findings
OL,6,FAn East Kent Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "We welcome the
OL,8,Fpublication of the interim findings of
OL,9,Fthe National Maternity and Neonatal
OL,10,FInvestigation and the opportunity to
OL,11,Fcontinue sharing our learning as we
OL,12,Fimprove maternity services in east
OL,13,FKent.
OL,15,F"We are sorry for the distress caused
OL,16,Fto every family we have failed in the
OL,17,Fpast. Our staff have made significant
OL,18,Fimprovements, and we remain committed
OL,19,Fto working towards providing the
OL,20,Fhighest standard of care for our
OL,21,Fcommunities."
OL,26,@}D@MO]
